        "description": "Blockers &amp; Breakers is a 2D escape maze strategy game. The player has to activate five switches and after that he can escape the maze. The maze changes its structure, so it will not be an easy task.<h3>How to play</h3>The goal of the game is to escape from the randomly changing maze. Escape the maze by activating 5 switches and opening the exit gate. After the first switch is activated, a second switch will appear. After the second switch is activated, a third switch will appear, etc. In the game are blockers. Blockers will block your progress through the maze. An additional blocker will appear every turn. Use breaker to break through the blocker. The breaker can break only one blocker and you are given only 10 breakers. Use them wisely. Score 1 point for each activated switch and bonus points for escaping with unused breakers.<h3>Game features</h3><ul><li>Every game is unique because the maze is randomly blocked</li><li>Challenging game, not easy to win</li><li>Suitable for all ages</li><li>Available for PC and mobile for free</li></ul>"
