        "description": "2048 is a classic logic game where puzzle is fun! Merge the numbers and get to the magical number we are all looking for - 2048! The objective of the game is to get the number 2048 using additions of the number two and its multipliers. Click to move the tiles from top to bottom or from bottom to top and from left to right or vice versa. When two tiles containing the same number are adjacent, they merge becoming one single tile. The numbers are added up automatically. When a tile is created with 2048, you've won! This game has three game modes: Classic, Time Out, and Intervention, and you can play it in three different sizes (classic, big, XL). For more dedicated players which are looking for a true challenge, you can merge the tiles to even bigger numbers, such as 4096, or 8192! Have fun.\n"
