        "description": "City Rider 3D is a 3D driving simulator, which take place in the huge city. The player can choose from different types of vehicles, e.g. truck, sports car, city car and many more.<h3>About Game</h3>Exactly what you want. An absolute freedom, a lot of various cars and a really large map of a city in which you can also find a terrain. Anyway, the most important is that you can change set up of each car! You can create a sport car from a truck or would you rather want to have sports like car with the heart of the truck? You can change everything and that's the great thing, which makes the game called City Rider 3d irresistible. Get ready to experience something fresh and new in the field of driving simulators. Have fun!<h3>Features</h3><ul><li>One huge city map with a freedom. Find city roads but also off-road ways.</li><li>You can choose one of the great cars. There is a total of seven cars in the game. Do you like Off-road, truck, sports car or city car?</li><li>Try something uncommon, change set up of your car.</li><li>Two angles of camera. Play from third person perspective or first person perspective.</li></ul><h3>City Rider 3D Unblocked</h3>If you have found City Rider 3D blocked on your electronic device, most likely this is due to blocking by network or device administrator (e.g. at a school). To play the game in this case you need to change the network or device you are connecting from. Find more info in our article: <a href=\"/blog/unblocked-games\" target=\"”_blank”\">Ways to avoid blocking?</a>"
